BEGIN:VEVENT
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://map-india.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Screenshot-2026-05-22-165600.png
CATEGORIES:Film Screenings,MAP,CBD
DTSTAMP:20260605T080608Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a weekend of queer short film screenings that bring into focus stories of identity\, resistance\, joy\, and community from across the country. Through intimate and thought-provoking narratives\, these films explore the realities of queer lives\, reflecting on visibility\, belonging\, resilience\, and self-expression in a time marked by increasing invisibilisation and protest.\n\nSpanning diverse experiences and perspectives\, the screenings invite audiences to engage with stories that challenge silence and reclaim space through the power of storytelling. Accompanied by conversations and reflections with speakers and community voices\, the programme creates space for dialogue rooted in solidarity\, and queer joy.\n\nThe film list is as follows.\n\n\n\nFilm Director\nFilm\nYear of Release\nLanguage in the Film\n\n\nKris\nNisha\n2025\nEnglish\, Hindi\, Malayalam\, Kannada\n\n\nDigvijay Andhorikar\nRoses Are...\n2025\nMarathi\n\n\nRaakesh\nAlmari Ka Achaar\nNot released yet\nHindi\n\n\nAshutosh S. Shankar\nTara\n2025\nHindi\, English\n\n\nDisha Bhardwaj\nChupi Roh\n2023\nHimachali/Hindi\n\n\nLeo Paapam\nDear Sahithya\n2024\nHindi English\n\n\nBonita Rajpurohit\nif you know you know\n2024\nEnglish\, Hindi\, Gujarati\n\n\nSnigdha Kapoor\nHoly Curse\n2024\nHindi\, English\n\n\nShashwat Dwivedi\nBobby Beauty Parlour\n2024\nHindi\n\n\nSudipto Kundu\nEnd of 14 Days\n2025\nBengali\n\n\n\n&nbsp\;\n\nThis programme is part of LGBTQIA+ programming and is an attempt to amplify narratives from within the queer community through film\, dialogue\, and collective reflection.
DTEND:20260607T113000Z
DTSTART:20260606T093000Z
SUMMARY:Queer Film Evenings
